# Rovr — Deployment, Chroma, and Production Ops

## Architecture (code vs index)

- **Git push / Railway redeploy** updates application code only — does **not** change chunk count.
- **Chroma index** lives on Railway persistent volume (`/app/chroma_db`) and S3 backup (`s3://experienceleaguechatbot/chroma_db/chroma_db.tar.gz`).
- **GHA** (`refresh-docs.yml`) updates S3 Chroma incrementally; Railway does **not** auto-sync from S3 unless volume is empty or `FORCE_CHROMA_RESTORE=true`.
- **Never upload local Chroma to S3** without verifying chunk count matches or exceeds production.

