## Local ingest pipeline

```bash
python scripts/sync_docs_to_s3.py --repo adobe-docs/customer-journey-analytics
python scripts/ingest_to_chroma.py --changed-only --product "Customer Journey Analytics"
python scripts/enrich_citation_metadata.py --changed-only --product "Customer Journey Analytics"
python scripts/upload_chroma_to_s3.py   # only when explicitly requested for prod
```

## Do NOT without explicit user request

- Upload Chroma to S3 or run Railway FORCE restore
- Commit `data/metadata_registry.json` without `git add -f`
- Use GHA `force=true` unless full rebuild is intentional (hours)
